data.description: Don't miss out on this Oleander Charmer! This adorable gem is tucked away, but still close to everything. Located conveniently near shopping, restaurants, and grocery stores. Easy access to freeways, and soon to connect to NW Bakersfield by way of the Westside Parkway. Tons of curb appeal and character, with original hardwood flooring, and Spanish architectural details throughout. 3 bedrooms plus a bonus room which can be used as a 4th bedroom, office, or formal dining room. Updated main bath, plus a half bathroom. Long driveway with plenty of room for parking, leading to a detached 1-car garage at the back of the property. -More photos coming soon!
